    "body": "Fixes #6331 \r\n\r\n```spack buildcache list``` has the following new flags:\r\n``` bash\r\n--show-flags          show spec compiler flags\r\n--show-full-compiler  show full compiler specs\r\n-v, --variants        show variants in output (can be long)\r\n```\r\n\r\nOutput\r\n``` bash\r\n# spack buildcache list apr-util\r\n==> Finding buildcaches in <MIRROR>/build_cache\r\n==> buildcache spec(s) matching 'apr-util'\r\n-- linux-centos7-x86_64 / gcc@4.8.5 -----------------------------\r\nev3wtha apr-util@1.6.0\r\n\r\n# spack buildcache list -v apr-util\r\n==> Finding buildcaches in <MIRROR>/build_cache\r\n==> buildcache spec(s) matching 'apr-util'\r\n-- linux-centos7-x86_64 / gcc@4.8.5 -----------------------------\r\nev3wtha apr-util@1.6.0+crypto~gdbm~odbc~pgsql~sqlite\r\n```",
